      <title>与伊朗的战争阐明了特朗普的支出重点：军事，而不是儿童保育</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/02/us/politics/trump-military-spending-budget.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在白宫准备发布 2027 年预算之际，特朗普总统表示，优先考虑的是军事保护，而不是社会计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/02/us/politics/trump-military-spending-budget.html</guid>
