    <item>
      <title>特朗普的代理司法部长托德·布兰奇是谁？</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/02/us/politics/todd-blanche-attorney-general-trump.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[虽然目前尚不清楚托德·布兰奇将在这个职位上呆多久，但无论谁最终永久接任，都将领导一个他按照自己的形象塑造的部门。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/02/us/politics/todd-blanche-attorney-general-trump.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 Apr 2026 20:34:13 GMT</pubDate>
