    <item>
      <title>特朗普表示他将在几周内结束伊朗战争。如果他不能怎么办？</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/02/us/politics/trump-speech-iran-war-whats-next.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普总统面临着一种可能性，即在他自己的两到三周的结束伊朗战争的窗口期结束时，一切都不会发生太大变化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/02/us/politics/trump-speech-iran-war-whats-next.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 Apr 2026 20:20:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
